{
  "stem": "26142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we didn't-- when they-- they-- they brought in everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we didn't see our brother, Eliezer, the oldest brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We didn't see him then, in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We found out five months later, that he was alone in his house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Because his wife and-- and the children were in Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "When they banged at his door, at the front door, there was an exit in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he somehow had a premonition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He-- he-- because this happened on Sunday night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And Friday, I remember in-- in during the day, he was in our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he said, I don't like what's going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He used to be-- when the Czechs were still there, he used to be a councilman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He was elected from the Zionist movement as a councilman in city council.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So he-- he- would get into the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he knew-- he knew the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He said, I knew the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I see there is something going on secretly that I wasn't invited.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I wasn't told.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they started banging at his door, he managed to put some clothing on and got out in the back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know that then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found out later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took a few days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He managed to escape and get reunited with his wife in Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so were left-- we were left, the three brothers, Moshe, Tsvi, and I, Moshe and his wife and the two children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tsvi's wife was with her parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know what's happening to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We also just found out five months later when we managed to come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
